data.description: Welcome home to 718 Holly Springs Drive! This 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home is located in the highly sought after community of River Plantation! Your new open concept home comes with a formal dining room open to the living room, kitchen, and breakfast nook. You will also have flex space on the first floor that can be used as a study, home office or playroom. The primary bedroom is located on the first floor and comes with 2 walk in closets, a bathroom with a shower, soaking tub, and double sink. Three additional well-appointed bedrooms are located upstairs offering comfort and versatility, while providing ample amount of space. The second bathroom is conveniently located to serve the upstairs bedrooms. 718 Holly Springs is conveniently located minutes from The Woodlands that has the best restaurants & shopping or you can head to Lake Conroe for a relaxing staycation!
